metadata.name: Social Dysfunction Edición Negra#1
metadata.description: The Irregular Wonderland™ is a messy, ambiguous, and complex environment to which is the world we live in. To see this Irregular Wonderland is dependent on our social cognitive abilities. Failure to see the complexities of this wonderland only contributes to the Social Dysfunction™ we experience on a scale seen at no other time in history.  Social Dysfunction™  is a digital art collection depicting the complexities of society, social identity, and other variables that create an Irregular Wonderland™.
